<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
  <meta charset="utf-8">
  <title>Workshop Registration Confirmation</title>
  <style>
    body {
      font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
      line-height: 1.6;
      color: #333;
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
    }
    .container {
      max-width: 600px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      padding: 20px;
    }
    .header {
      background-color: #f0e6ff;
      padding: 20px;
      text-align: center;
      border-radius: 5px 5px 0 0;
    }
    .content {
      background-color: #fff;
      padding: 20px;
      border: 1px solid #ddd;
    }
    .footer {
      background-color: #f5f5f5;
      padding: 15px;
      text-align: center;
      font-size: 12px;
      color: #666;
      border-radius: 0 0 5px 5px;
    }
    h1 {
      color: #722ed1;
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
    }
    h2 {
      color: #333;
      margin-top: 20px;
    }
    .highlight {
      color: #722ed1;
      font-weight: bold;
    }
    .button {
      display: inline-block;
      padding: 10px 20px;
      background-color: #722ed1;
      color: #fff;
      text-decoration: none;
      border-radius: 5px;
      margin: 20px 0;
    }
    .status {
      padding: 8px 12px;
      border-radius: 4px;
      display: inline-block;
      font-weight: bold;
    }
    .status-pending {
      background-color: #faad14;
      color: #fff;
    }
    .status-completed {
      background-color: #52c41a;
      color: #fff;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="container">
    <div class="header">
      <h1>Workshop Registration Confirmation</h1>
    </div>
    <div class="content">
      <p>Dear <span class="highlight">{{name}}</span>,</p>
      
      <p>Thank you for registering for our Psychology Workshop! We're excited to have you join us.</p>
      
      <h2>Registration Details</h2>
      <p>
        <strong>Payment Status:</strong> 
        <span class="status {{#if isPending}}status-pending{{else}}status-completed{{/if}}">
          {{paymentStatus}}
        </span>
      </p>
      
      <p><strong>Workshop Dates:</strong> {{workshopDetails.dates}}</p>
      <p><strong>Workshop Timing:</strong> {{workshopDetails.timing}}</p>
      
      {{#if isPending}}
      <p><strong>Next Steps:</strong> Please complete your payment using the UPI link that was provided during registration. After payment, upload the screenshot to complete your registration.</p>
      {{else}}
      <p><strong>Next Steps:</strong> Your registration is complete! We will send you the workshop details closer to the date.</p>
      {{/if}}
      
      <p>If you have any questions or need assistance, please reply to this email.</p>
      
      <p>Best regards,<br>Dr. Agarwal's Team</p>
    </div>
    <div class="footer">
      <p>This is an automated email. Please do not reply directly to this message.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html> 